  "description": "Block-storage control-plane health for an OpenStack deployment scraped by openstack-exporter: are the cinder-volume, cinder-scheduler and cinder-backup services up, and are any volumes stuck in error or creating? Leads with services down and volumes in error — the two signals that mean tenants can't get storage.",
